<DocsLayout title="Cleo" description="Cleo Design System — documentation for Quiet Authority">
  <div class="prose">
    <h1>Cleo</h1>
    <hr class="section-accent-rule" />
    <p class="page-lead">
      Documentation for a product built for physical therapists who are still charting at 10pm — and
      deserve to be home for dinner on a Tuesday.
    </p>
    <p>
      Cleo is AI-assisted documentation and denial prevention for outpatient physical therapy. This
      site is not a marketing page. It is a living reference for the design language and the
      emotional philosophy behind every decision in the product.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every token, component, and pattern documented here exists in service of one moment: a
      therapist walking through their front door while the sun is still up, for the first time in
      two years.
    </p>

    <h2>Start here</h2>
    <ul>
