      <li><a href="/foundations/color">Color tokens</a> — the complete palette</li>
      <li><a href="/art">Logo & brand art</a> — approved identity assets</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to use this system</h2>
    <p>
      Designers: start with foundations and the journey mapping. Engineers: use tokens and component
      specs as the source of truth. Copywriters: read voice and tone before writing a single
      headline. Everyone: ask whether the work makes a burned-out, skeptical PT feel understood
      before they feel sold to.
    </p>
